    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a dependable daily driver for someone who prioritizes mechanical reliability over cosmetic perfection. The exterior shows its age with some noticeable scratches, a few small door dings, and minor paint fading on the hood. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and a small tear on the driver's seat, though all essential electronics and climate controls are functioning properly. It has been regularly serviced, runs well, and is ready for the road, though it is certainly not a show car.",
