    {
      "id": "sybil_19_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_19",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with this absolute gem of a car. It\u2019s been so reliable for me and still drives like a dream! It\u2019s in really nice shape and has been well-loved, making it the perfect companion for your daily commutes or weekend getaways. I\u2019m looking for a smooth, easy sale to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. Come take it for a spin\u2014you won't be disappointed!",
