    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_18_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_18",
      "description": "This vehicle is a standout example of pride in ownership. The exterior paint retains a deep, glossy finish, showing only the minor, inevitable signs of careful road use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and smoke-free, with all electronic features and climate controls functioning perfectly. Mechanically, the car is robust; it has benefited from a consistent maintenance schedule, resulting in a smooth transmission, responsive brakes, and a quiet, comfortable ride. It is a turn-key vehicle that offers the perfect balance of aesthetic appeal and mechanical reliability, ready for its next long-term owner.",
