    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my reliable daily driver, and it's honestly been such a champ. It's been well-loved and taken care of, so it's still looking great and ready to hit the road for many more miles. Whether you're heading out on a road trip or just cruising around town, this car is a total joy to drive. I'm looking for a smooth sale, so come by, say hi, and take it for a spin\u2014you're going to love it!",
