    {
      "id": "sybil_21_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_21",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8, renowned for its 8,400 RPM redline and eight individual throttle bodies. The powertrain is mated to a precise 6-speed manual transmission, distributing torque through a Variable M Differential Lock. The chassis geometry remains sharp, utilizing aluminum subframes to minimize unsprung weight, while the factory carbon fiber roof lowers the center of gravity for superior lateral dynamics. Critical preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service, has been documented, ensuring the high-strung valvetrain remains within factory tolerances. This is a mechanically sound specimen offering a raw, analog driving experience and a signature high-frequency induction note.",
